name: Paizuri Focus
description:
Would appreciate images, feedback, requests, reviews, and of course comments in the comments. Please check out my other models if you like this one.

A checkpoint based off NAI trained on 175 Images of various Paizuri.

Later versions will have a larger dataset, the first one was just a test.

paizuri and, paizuri related tags should help, if anyone knows a better model to train of off please let me know. I have not tested using paizuri Loras so don't know if they help or not. can make decent images that aren't paizuri (if you like the way NAI/basic illustrations look)

characters are tagged, and some variants of paizuri, other versions may tag artists and train them as multiple concepts. don't know if Over_clothes_paizuri or Reverse_paizuri were tagged in V1. seems to like to generate simple backgrounds. it is mergeable but don't know how well. a lot of the images are currently flagged sop they won't pop up.

recommended tags: paizuri, cooperative_paizuri

optional tags: pov, from_side, 1girl, 2girls, 1boy, cum, fellatio, oral, unaligned_breasts, symmetrical_docking, asymmetrical_docking, breast_lift, breast_hold, and similar tags

from my testing using paizuri Loras looks good, some character Loras might be iffy

modelVersions.description:
read 0.5's description as well. Second Version of the model, should be more varied and more consistent with the tags, still probably not the greatest but it is better than the first version. sadly I once again messed up on some of the captions so it is a little off sometimes. I also think uncensored penises look more weird in this version. can be merged with other checkpoints, Merging can help the weird penises and potentially boring artstyle.

main focus of this version was getting under and over clothes paizuri to work, it's not perfect but it is more consistent.
